2. cs.GR (Graphics) is also likely as the paper discusses the development of a VR application, which involves graphics and visual design. 
3. cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity and Privacy) is a possible category as the paper may touch upon security and privacy concerns related to the use of VR technology. 
4. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is less likely as the paper does not seem to focus on algorithmic complexity or computational theory. 
5. cs.ROBOTS (Robotics) is also less likely as the paper does not involve the design or development of physical robots.
